		"description": "<p><em>Passive: You gain advantage on Strength (Athletics) checks made to shove or grapple creatures larger than you as well as an expertise die when attacking creatures bigger than you.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Titan’s Fall:</strong> When you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you may expend a Legend Die to attempt to knock it down. The target must succeed on a Strength saving throw (Maneuver DC) or be knocked [[/condition id=prone]] and take extra damage equal to the result.</p>",
