			"description": "<ul><li><p>A prone creature's only movement option is to crawl (every 1 foot of movement while crawling costs 1 extra foot) until it stands up.</p></li><li><p>Standing up requires half a creature’s movement.</p></li><li><p>A prone creature makes melee attack rolls with disadvantage.</p></li><li><p>An attack roll against a prone creature is made with advantage if the attacker is within 5 feet. Otherwise, the attack roll is made with disadvantage.</p></li></ul>",
